channel.title: In search of an experienced developer
channel.description:
Hello guys.
For the project I am starting with Streetwave a r-s mod, named Concretion, we need a server developer. You think you can fit in our team? Please fill in this application form and I'll decide if you're capable.;) Also we are not looking for amateur programmers and you will be paid.
[b]You need at least 2 years of experience with Java/programming RSPS! We'll also set some agreements.[/b]
[code]Name: Age: Years of experience with Java: How many hours a day are you able to program?: Why do you want to be a developer at Concretion?:[/code]
